	   <tr><td colspan=2>I recently made an Erudite SK, and I have made 5th level, and I am wondering about my immediate future. So here are some questions.<br><br>Can an SK get through Erude, I know that necros cannot go through the town normally, and dont know how they get to the boat. If a SK has the same faction problems, How do they get to the boat. I know how to get OFF the boat, and through Qeynos aquaducts. <br><br>How are Erudite SK's recieved in the "evil" cities, as Erudes are not an evil race? Which SK guilds may I enter?&nbsp;&nbsp;Am I KOS in Neriak? Grobb? Ogguk? I worship Cazic Thule, am I still KOS in Cab? What about Overthere? <br><br>I know when you play an evil race, and an evil class, you can travel in evil cities (except Cab) without being killed everywhere (though Ogre warriors are killed in the arena at Neriak Foriegn quarter by the Ogres) I realise there are some sensitive places, but I am asking in General, how are the evil classes recieved by the evil races? <br><br>Thanks alot. <br><br>Tiorsdan<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
