	   <tr><td colspan=2>Youll be fine in erudin. As far as evil cities go your out of luck with the exception of neriak(which seems to be rather out of the way considering freeport is right next door).&nbsp;&nbsp;There are guides to improving faction in cabilis but it looked like more of a pain in the arse than it was worth. Freeport is dubious but safe for sk even after killing 4 guards for darkforge. In the Overthere you can buy sell bank get food and drink spells bandages etc. One thing about Overthere, if you like banking in kunark do not kill ogres in Timorous Deep or hunt in karnors. Overthere faction is Venril Sathir which can only be reversed by killing lvl 60 mobs. I found out the hard way and can only sell to the greedy iksar merchant by the mudhole towards warsliks woods (gives maybe half of what id get at gypsy camp in or inn at oasis) I managed to stop killing before i was KOS there and can at least put stuff in bank, but thats all I can do there now. The only sk guilds ive ever had to use are freeport and paineel.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
